The transition is not smooth yet, I'm trying to figure out some math to help the transition.
Also the blending mode is set to normal now because I didn't have any blending nodes that worked with batches.

Ideally I'd like to implement a way to do inference on only x+y number of frames, where x is number of frames / 2, and y is the overlaying frames.

I couldn't figure out the math yet, so instead I'm doing inference on all the frames and picking five subset of frames (starting, overlay 1, overlay 2, overlay 3, end) and applying incrementing blending.

You can change the Checkpoint (1.5 only since we're using AnimateDiff), but not the LoRAs.

If you want to try porting this to SDXL or Flux, you'll most probably need to figure out a way to implement temporal consisntency that doesn't involve AnimateDiff.

Place the LoRAs in the /models/loras folder

The original workflow used both Depth and Lineart.
I prefer using Depth only at a lowish strength as it allows the "growings" to appear more organic because they're less bound by the controlnet while still being guided by it.
I left this AnimateDiff stack the same as in the original workflow.
First generation pass, followed by a RIFE frame interpolation pass for adding smoothness and more frames.

This is the main group for Z-Depth manipulation.
First the frames are resized, then the subject's mask is extracted for each frame. The same happens for Depth.
Then both the starting Z-Depth front and back planes are moved from arbitrary starting points, and their intersection with the subject mask creates an animated mask that acts as inpainting guidance for each frame.

Models:
Loras (place them in ./ComfyUI/models/loras):
- https://huggingface.co/wangfuyun/AnimateLCM/blob/main/AnimateLCM_sd15_t2v_lora.safetensors
- https://huggingface.co/naonovn/Lora/blob/main/add_detail.safetensors
- https://huggingface.co/Lykon/LoRA/blob/7b44164cabdc9a4f34b4ef27f508dacde0a540e0/animemix_v3_offset.safetensors
AnimateDiff Evolved Lora (place them in ./ComfyUI/custom_nodes/ComfyUI-AnimateDiff-Evolved/motion-lora):
- https://huggingface.co/peteromallet/poms-funtime-mlora-emporium/blob/main/LiquidAF-0-1.safetensors
AnimateDiff Evolved Checkpoint (place them in ./ComfyUI/custom_nodes/ComfyUI-AnimateDiff-Evolved/models):
- https://huggingface.co/wangfuyun/AnimateLCM/blob/main/AnimateLCM_sd15_t2v.ckpt

Input the video here, and select:
- how many frames you want
- how many frames to skip
- the frames to select every nth frame (1 = every frame, 4 = 1 frame every 4 frames)

This group enables Feature manipulation and visualizes the time / z-depth movement graph.

Change scale_type for different graphs and z-depth movement behaviours.
